.TH WLAB 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wlab \- WLA DX binary-to-WLA-DB converter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wlab
.B \-[ap]{bdh}
.I binfile
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wlab
reads a binary file and outputs its contents as WLA DX assembler source
(a WLA DB directive block), suitable for inclusion in WLA DX assembly projects.
.SH OPTIONS
.SS Commands (one required)
.TP
.B b
Output binary (raw bytes).
.TP
.B d
Output decimal.
.TP
.B h
Output hexadecimal.
.SS Options
.TP
.B a
Print address alongside each value.
.TP
.B p
Skip the binary file header.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Convert a binary file to hex WLA DB:
.PP
.RS
.B wlab \-h binary.bin
.RE
.PP
Convert a binary file to hex WLA DB with addresses:
.PP
.RS
.B wlab \-ah binary.bin
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
